platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 用 Apple Pencil 書寫更流暢

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Sure, the handwriting experience in Penbook is best-in-class. And yes, we love how Live Paper puts our Calendar events in an agenda alongside our sketches and scribbles. But what really keeps us coming back is how the app obsesses over customization, from paper and pen types to templates that have completely changed the way we take notes.
A best-in-class handwriting experience. Extensive customisation, from paper and pen types to templates completely change the way we take notes.

Une expérience d’écriture de pointe grâce à la personnalisation du type de papier ou de stylo, en plus des modèles qui changent totalement votre manière de prendre des notes.
這個筆記 App 提供多元自訂選項，包括紙張和筆的種類，以及各式各樣的範本，徹底改變我們寫筆記的方式，打造一流的手寫體驗。
